<subSubSection id="C337088DF761B120B182FDB830E04417" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F761B120B182FDB831B84057" blockId="20.[151,1437,511,789]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">
<collectionCode id="ED3CC3C3F761B120B182FDB832C2411C" box="[199,251,583,609]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">TYPE</collectionCode>
MATERIAL: Sundevall, in his original description (1850: 99) gave no indication that he had more than a single female at hand. However, Sundevall’s acquisition catalogue indicated that he had 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF761B120B5E7FD94377A41C7" box="[1186,1347,619,645]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" type="generic">six specimens</specimenCount>
that he identified as 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F761B120B068FD7033D741EB" box="[301,494,655,681]" class="Aves" family="Alaudidae" genus="Alauda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="cheniana">
<emphasis id="B9598714F761B120B068FD7033D741EB" box="[301,494,655,681]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">Alauda cheniana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but he later changed his mind and decided that 
<specimenCount id="9D2B908FF761B120B561FD70368641EB" box="[1060,1215,655,681]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
belonged to a new undescribed species close to 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F761B120B09FFD4C3093418E" authorityName="Sundevall" authorityYear="1850" box="[474,682,691,717]" class="Aves" family="Alaudidae" genus="Alauda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="conirostris">
<emphasis id="B9598714F761B120B09FFD4C3093418E" box="[474,682,691,717]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">Alauda conirostris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This specimen should be treated as the single specimen in the type series and is a 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F761B120B07BFD28339A41B3" box="[318,419,727,753]" pageId="20" pageNumber="541">holotype</typeStatus>
, catalogue number NRM 569768 [6453], a study skin of an adult female collected 
<date id="FF937DC6F761B120B40EFD2832EB4057" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" value="1843-07-12">12 July 1843</date>
. See comments below for a discussion on geographical origin.
</paragraph>
<caption id="DF520B8EF761B120B1D2F92E30C3444F" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6541745" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6541745" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6541745/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="541" startId="20.[151,250,1745,1769]" targetBox="[151,1436,810,1719]" targetPageId="20">
